looks quite clean.

21
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:13,880
Your Highness.

22
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,040
I got it!

23
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,480
It's water!

24
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,320
Your Majesty,

25
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:25,840
based on my careful investigation,

26
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,600
the cause of the premature delivery

27
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,440
lies in the water used for decoction.

28
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:31,280
Someone secretly replaced it

29
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,960
with water boiled in a copper pot.

30
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,880
What's wrong with

31
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,520
that?

32
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,360
Water boiled in a copper pot

33
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:40,280
will greatly change the nature of herbs,

34
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:41,680
making them harmful.

35
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:45,120
Moreover, this method cannot
be detected with a silver needle.

36
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,680
Someone replaced
the water used for decoction

37
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,320
with water boiled in a copper pot,

38
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:52,120
and I unknowingly used it.

39
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,160
In this way,

40
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,120
it is the same as making a decoction
in a copper pot,

41
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:56,920
which

42
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,960
caused the Princess Consort's
premature delivery.

43
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,480
I can't believe it.

44
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:01,800
Do you know

45
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:02,880
who did it?

46
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,960
Your Majesty,

47
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:06,440
I don't know.

48
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:09,880
Your Majesty,

49
