222
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,360
After I discovered the problem,

223
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,080
I secretly asked Officer Song to

224
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,520
replace the water you used

225
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,280
for making tea and tonic soup

226
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,320
with water boiled in a copper pot.

227
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,840
Look at you,

228
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,080
your hair is falling out.

229
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:42,320
How dare you say it's not poisonous?
